import { ThunderboltOutlined, HomeOutlined, YoutubeOutlined } from "@ant-design/icons"

export const HOME = "/"
export const DASHBOARD = "/dashboard"
export const LOGIN = "/login"
export const TODO = "/todos"
export const WEATHER = "/weather"
export const FORGOT_PASSWORD = "/forgot_password"

export const PUBLIC_ROUTES = [LOGIN, FORGOT_PASSWORD]

export const ROUTES = [
  {
    path: DASHBOARD,
    icon: YoutubeOutlined,
    name: "Dashboard",
  },
  {
    path: WEATHER,
    icon: ThunderboltOutlined,
    name: "Weather",
  },
]
